        - Unblocks: std library result.0/result.1 pattern, multiple return values

[x] 2. `either` reduction rule (if/else at runtime)
        - CPU worker_thread: BRANCH ~ NUM fires, selects true/false, erases loser
        - NODE_BRANCH=7 added to encoding (to be folded into ω via A3)
        - TODO(A1): GPU kernel parity via unified pic.reduce pass

[/] 3. Beta-reduction (function application at runtime)
        - Phase 1: γ(+,f) ~ γ(-,f) wires aux ports (p1↔p1, p2↔p2) — this PR
        - TODO(A3): collapse checkBeta into standard annihilation
        - TODO(A1): GPU kernel parity via unified pic.reduce pass
        - Phase 2: body-graph cloning for multi-arg / closures

[x] 4. mlir-op full pipeline connection
